Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.30,0:01:31.15,OP,,0,0,0,,在心灵的街道中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.67,0:01:37.50,OP,,0,0,0,,闪耀着希望之光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.10,0:01:43.70,OP,,0,0,0,,用虚幻的羽翼挥动着梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.40,0:01:49.95,OP,,0,0,0,,是你与我寻找的目标
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.27,0:02:06.47,OP,,0,0,0,,真理总是隐藏在眼中 蓝蓝的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.82,0:02:13.32,OP,,0,0,0,,我们要往何处去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.20,0:02:20.12,OP,,0,0,0,,俩人未来与现今的流浪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.42,0:02:25.75,OP,,0,0,0,,我们继续踏上旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.80,0:02:32.62,OP,,0,0,0,,永远的目标地 无止尽的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.97,0:02:43.62,OP,,0,0,0,,希望能不放手不断追寻 直到永远
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.92,0:03:30.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,箭书
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.73,0:03:37.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.37,0:03:39.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挑战书
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.87,0:03:45.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷兽…苍天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.67,0:03:48.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这正是叙述我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.18,0:03:52.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不断战斗之宿命的序章
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.39,0:04:02.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第68话 给七宝充满愤怒的挑战书
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.98,0:04:26.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,苍天少主
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.92,0:04:30.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挑战书已经确实送到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.19,0:04:34.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一刻终于来临了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.59,0:04:40.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我红龙是多么的期盼这一天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.10,0:04:42.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,苍天少主
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.46,0:04:44.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请以身为雷兽一族最后一人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.80,0:04:46.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发挥全力奋战到底吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.44,0:04:54.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么什么  给七宝殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.01,0:04:56.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赌上雷兽一族的自尊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.11,0:04:59.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,堂堂正正要求和你决斗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.05,0:05:03.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今日傍晚我在雷鸣谷等你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.45,0:05:04.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃跑的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.42,0:05:06.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同伴们将性命不保
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.02,0:05:08.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是挑战书吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.23,0:05:13.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷鸣谷的话  就在这附近呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.16,0:05:16.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先前雷兽兄弟住的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.50,0:05:18.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是飞天满天的亲戚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.40,0:05:21.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然送这种东西过来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.14,0:05:22.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙胆子真不小
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.30,0:05:25.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  不要随便看别人的信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.97,0:05:27.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  这件事好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.54,0:05:28.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.68,0:05:31.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果为了报雷兽一族的仇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.48,0:05:32.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该不是七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.08,0:05:36.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是直接跟那两人\N交手的犬夜叉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.78,0:05:38.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.35,0:05:40.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一定是因为犬夜叉只是半妖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.79,0:05:42.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷兽根本看不上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.52,0:05:43.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.53,0:05:46.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.29,0:05:47.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.73,0:05:50.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算和这个\N叫做苍天的雷兽决斗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.43,0:05:52.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是没办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.93,0:05:54.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我为了替父亲报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.80,0:05:58.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想不到在那之前\N就出现了找我报仇的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.04,0:06:00.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是战斗之人的宿命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.51,0:06:02.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在耍什么帅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.44,0:06:04.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少因为自己没办法耍帅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.95,0:06:06.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在那里酸葡萄
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.51,0:06:07.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.88,0:06:09.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么需要我助你一臂之力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.82,0:06:11.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮你打个折…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.05,0:06:12.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有需要的话别客气尽管说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.95,0:06:15.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要介绍美女给我就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.06,0:06:17.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两人啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.83,0:06:21.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管发生什么事\N我都不会帮你忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.53,0:06:22.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用你操心了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.76,0:06:24.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,区区的雷兽我马上就打跑他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.21,0:06:32.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是雷兽兄弟住过的山谷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.84,0:06:34.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不寻常的妖气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.78,0:06:36.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是没变
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.58,0:06:38.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有那里天气恶劣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.28,0:06:41.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝  不要逞强了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.58,0:06:43.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他们帮你如何
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.28,0:06:44.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.42,0:06:45.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是这样做的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.65,0:06:48.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接受决斗的我面子该往哪摆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.23,0:06:51.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么面子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.56,0:06:53.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在你那张光会说的嘴挨打之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.10,0:06:57.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子根本不行嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.60,0:06:58.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该不行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.93,0:07:00.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.24,0:07:02.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,苍天少主
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.80,0:07:05.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从刚才您一直在写什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.11,0:07:10.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红龙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.25,0:07:12.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要老是飘在那  过来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.51,0:07:13.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.82,0:07:20.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些是这次的作战书
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.12,0:07:22.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牢牢的记在脑子里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.32,0:07:23.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作战?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.52,0:07:26.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是堂堂正正的决斗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.90,0:07:29.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像我这么可爱的小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.90,0:07:32.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能打赢\N那些穷凶恶极的邪魔歪道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.77,0:07:33.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.27,0:07:35.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个叫弥勒的法师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.90,0:07:38.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拥有什么都能吸进去的风穴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.04,0:07:40.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个叫珊瑚的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.64,0:07:42.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是驱魔的高手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.64,0:07:45.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且她还收服了一只\N叫做云母的妖怪猫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.41,0:07:46.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.15,0:07:48.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为全都是我去调查的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.55,0:07:52.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤其是这个犬夜叉\N与戈薇是最强的双人组
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.55,0:07:55.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道有多少妖怪被他们打败吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.42,0:07:55.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.06,0:07:58.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正面冲突的话我就没命了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.56,0:07:59.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是真的发生这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.49,0:08:02.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷兽一族就会完全毁灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.36,0:08:04.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就这样隐居起来不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.93,0:08:06.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.30,0:08:07.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们是我最大的仇人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.80,0:08:10.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少要找七宝要报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.64,0:08:13.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再咯哩叭唆的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.07,0:08:14.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点去实行战术
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.68,0:08:16.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们已经来到这附近了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.45,0:08:18.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.25,0:08:27.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.76,0:08:28.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.69,0:08:31.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要边发抖边走路啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.03,0:08:32.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.69,0:08:34.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别激动别激动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.46,0:08:35.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.83,0:08:38.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话傍晚之前会到不了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.47,0:08:40.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挑战书不是这样子写吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.70,0:08:42.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  挑战书
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.47,0:08:47.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.34,0:08:48.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.61,0:08:51.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个只能念“七宝”吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.71,0:08:52.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.98,0:08:54.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有没有别的念法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.92,0:08:56.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,例如“犬夜叉”之类的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.99,0:09:00.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你连自己的名字都不会念吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.56,0:09:01.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要把我当笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.42,0:09:02.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是确认一下而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.86,0:09:03.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啦  没错  就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.99,0:09:05.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是给我的挑战书啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.86,0:09:10.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等着瞧  苍天  我马上就到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.73,0:09:13.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝…你根本没有前进
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.74,0:09:15.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再也忍不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.50,0:09:17.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.75,0:09:28.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们大家听好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.02,0:09:30.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次真的不用出手帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.22,0:09:32.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁要帮你的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.75,0:09:34.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了好了  快点走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.52,0:09:35.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.72,0:09:37.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对方是穷凶恶极的雷兽一族
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.03,0:09:38.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.76,0:09:40.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你快找个安全的地方避难吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.10,0:09:42.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好~好~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.33,0:09:43.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚与弥勒也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.17,0:09:46.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他非常希望我们帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.53,0:09:47.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.27,0:09:50.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坦白的拜托不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.75,0:10:03.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先利用大岩石
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.15,0:10:06.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将七宝和犬夜叉他们分开
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.59,0:10:13.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.76,0:10:16.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.73,0:10:18.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那小子在搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.77,0:10:28.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进行的很顺利呢  苍天少主
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.28,0:10:32.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了对了  我都忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.35,0:10:33.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变身
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.76,0:10:42.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.69,0:10:44.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.03,0:10:46.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个迷糊虫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.13,0:10:47.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被逮到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.26,0:10:48.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快追
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.16,0:10:50.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  拿他没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.80,0:10:53.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭家伙  快点放我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.77,0:10:56.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来得正好  七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.41,0:11:03.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像你这种杂碎对我没有用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.41,0:11:05.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫老大出来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.45,0:11:07.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去叫雷兽一族的苍天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.68,0:11:09.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.89,0:11:11.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你骗人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.72,0:11:14.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才没骗人  看就知道了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.32,0:11:16.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是看了不知道才问啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.83,0:11:19.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛  真可笑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.43,0:11:21.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有闲功夫跟小鬼玩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.73,0:11:22.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.60,0:11:24.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要把我当成小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.03,0:11:25.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.31,0:11:35.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有好东西嘛  交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.11,0:11:37.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧  明明就是小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.45,0:11:38.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对不对不对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.61,0:11:40.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你才是小孩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.48,0:11:42.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么  我可是了不起的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.82,0:11:44.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.12,0:11:45.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要咯哩叭唆  把那个给我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.95,0:11:46.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.92,0:11:48.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说给我就给我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.59,0:11:49.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说不要就是不要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.69,0:11:52.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这两人根本就还是小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.96,0:11:55.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红龙  你还有事情要做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.73,0:11:57.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是的  没错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.27,0:12:02.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.48,0:12:15.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来要封住云母
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.78,0:12:17.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是妖怪但是猫还是猫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.62,0:12:19.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用木天蓼应该就能迷住它了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.72,0:12:24.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歪脑筋动得还真快
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.46,0:12:31.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  云母
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.17,0:12:34.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个气味是木天蓼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.24,0:12:35.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.88,0:12:43.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是对方的陷阱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.48,0:12:46.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子接下来得用走的了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.38,0:12:51.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么了  小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.92,0:12:54.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你们  请救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.32,0:12:57.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法师  这有点可疑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.29,0:12:59.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不觉得是陷阱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.39,0:13:02.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚  我是遵循着佛道之人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.76,0:13:04.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是任何情况
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.07,0:13:07.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都无法眼睁睁看着\N有困难的人不管的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.27,0:13:08.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算这是个陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.64,0:13:10.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也会高兴的接受的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.07,0:13:14.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还真是大好人呢  法师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.81,0:13:16.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒的弱点就是女人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.01,0:13:19.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而珊瑚绝不会丢下弥勒不管
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.71,0:13:22.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利用这一点就能制服他们两人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.55,0:13:25.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻烦…请你再靠近一点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.05,0:13:28.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  我当然会过去的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.29,0:13:30.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法师不要这个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.46,0:13:33.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来  方便的话将原委…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.73,0:13:41.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好很好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.80,0:13:43.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早就跟你说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.94,0:13:45.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.21,0:13:46.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是法师害的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.74,0:13:48.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.84,0:13:50.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快放我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.48,0:13:51.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是要决斗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.05,0:13:54.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挑拨对我是没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.98,0:13:55.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.12,0:13:58.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,送这个来的不是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.35,0:13:59.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.22,0:14:01.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是引诱你出来的陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.59,0:14:02.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然是陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.49,0:14:06.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算怎么对付我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.19,0:14:09.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要慢慢折磨你到死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.56,0:14:10.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.40,0:14:15.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哭吧  喊叫吧  怕的浑身发抖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.60,0:14:17.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.11,0:14:21.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此  你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.01,0:14:23.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很弱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.58,0:14:26.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才会逃避决斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.15,0:14:30.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算你厉害识破了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.48,0:14:32.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我的头脑聪明得很
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.52,0:14:33.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了弥补弱点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.85,0:14:36.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我早已设下\N如此天衣无缝的战术了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.76,0:14:38.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太肮脏了  你这卑劣的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.29,0:14:38.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.03,0:14:41.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你才是靠同伴帮忙的胆小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.90,0:14:43.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才没有拜托他们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.26,0:14:44.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是他们自己要跟来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.77,0:14:46.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再找借口了  胆小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.13,0:14:47.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要叫我胆小鬼  卑劣的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.64,0:14:49.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胆小胆小胆小胆小
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.44,0:14:52.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卑鄙卑劣卑劣卑劣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.88,0:14:57.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒他们在搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.18,0:14:58.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的好慢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.15,0:15:01.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好  来了来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.45,0:15:03.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉最怕的\N就是戈薇的“坐下”
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.65,0:15:04.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这招一定管用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.15,0:15:08.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.79,0:15:13.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐下坐下坐下坐下坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.90,0:15:15.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.43,0:15:17.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么戈薇的“坐下”没有效
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.67,0:15:18.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.40,0:15:20.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是把那个当作是我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.27,0:15:21.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很像不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.70,0:15:23.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里像了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.30,0:15:26.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭家伙  你做好觉悟了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.17,0:15:28.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.64,0:15:31.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多该回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.58,0:15:33.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住  想逃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.91,0:15:35.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.79,0:15:40.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样  投降了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.42,0:15:43.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少罗唆  你才该快点投降呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.96,0:15:47.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你拿的画笔好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.36,0:15:48.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.20,0:15:50.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是戈薇送给我的\N叫做蜡笔的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.17,0:15:53.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好  那个给我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.97,0:15:54.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.84,0:15:56.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么关系  小气鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.57,0:15:57.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.84,0:15:58.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是你放我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.87,0:16:01.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我或许可以考虑一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.88,0:16:08.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样  很漂亮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.95,0:16:11.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想要好想要好想要好想要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.72,0:16:13.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就快点放我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.85,0:16:15.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不会上你的当
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.96,0:16:18.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要慢慢的宰了你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.83,0:16:20.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么决斗赢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.59,0:16:22.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就可以得到这蜡笔  怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.20,0:16:24.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这倒是好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.77,0:16:30.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这小子也许是白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.87,0:16:33.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是稀奇  会飞的蛇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.51,0:16:34.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是龙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.38,0:16:36.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少装模作样了  小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.75,0:16:39.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙是雷兽的使魔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.78,0:16:40.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有礼貌!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.48,0:16:42.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是大名鼎鼎龙族的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.92,0:16:45.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟你说不要装模作样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.29,0:16:46.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  只要再一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.02,0:16:49.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭家伙  你当我的头是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.99,0:16:50.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少罗唆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.23,0:16:53.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好  这样就能逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.03,0:16:55.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  就别再欺负他了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.93,0:16:57.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他也蛮可怜的不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.23,0:17:01.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇你太多嘴了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.40,0:17:02.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不需要同情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.94,0:17:04.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再怎么说我也是龙族
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.04,0:17:06.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想打的话尽量打吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.41,0:17:09.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也有些优点嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.04,0:17:12.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惨了  反而自找麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.95,0:17:14.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,苍天在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.28,0:17:15.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝也在那里对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.42,0:17:18.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁会说那种事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.29,0:17:21.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛  臭小子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.06,0:17:22.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.89,0:17:27.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.56,0:17:29.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吓到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.90,0:17:33.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只要打头三次就能变身
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.07,0:17:36.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来啊来啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.10,0:17:37.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶\N来啊来啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.10,0:17:39.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来啊来啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.44,0:17:42.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一开始就来这招不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.95,0:17:50.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没用的  没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.95,0:17:51.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.95,0:17:53.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铁碎牙竟然没有用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.19,0:17:58.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  犬夜叉  觉悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.60,0:18:05.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做好觉悟了吗  七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.87,0:18:07.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我的台词吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.24,0:18:09.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.14,0:18:20.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来啊来啊来啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.85,0:18:22.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.02,0:18:26.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对手是云  风之伤也不行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.89,0:18:29.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.82,0:18:34.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁现在  先收拾这小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.00,0:18:40.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.67,0:18:48.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.01,0:18:51.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.91,0:18:53.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接招  狐火
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.11,0:18:58.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那算什么  雷击
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.02,0:19:03.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么  想不到你还蛮强的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.92,0:19:07.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这还用说  你以为我是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.33,0:19:09.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好  现在开始要认真了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.00,0:19:10.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.70,0:19:14.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.27,0:19:17.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中了我的箭也撑不了多久的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.81,0:19:20.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  你不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.54,0:19:24.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.98,0:19:26.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本就没事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.21,0:19:28.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那光箭只是中看不中用
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.08,0:19:32.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么  这怎么可能  接招
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.76,0:19:37.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碰到也无所谓  刺一下手看看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.36,0:19:43.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.83,0:19:45.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个拿来治肩酸也许不错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.83,0:19:46.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.97,0:19:47.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是老太婆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.74,0:19:50.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有逃走算你倒霉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.61,0:19:54.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙\N只要揍三下就能变身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.48,0:19:55.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有说过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.61,0:19:56.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少装蒜了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.58,0:20:01.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  好过分喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.59,0:20:06.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  你就带我们去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.05,0:20:08.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个叫苍天的所在的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.60,0:20:17.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有两把刷子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.10,0:20:20.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.67,0:20:22.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狐妖术  旋转独乐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.00,0:20:25.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷兽幻术  达摩不倒翁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.08,0:20:31.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此只好使出爱哭香菇了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.31,0:20:34.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我就用爆笑粟子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.23,0:20:50.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,苍天  你就放弃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.90,0:20:52.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少罗唆  你才是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.67,0:20:54.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,性命跟蜡笔哪一个比较重要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.90,0:20:55.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.24,0:20:57.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  你们没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.67,0:21:00.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.98,0:21:03.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红龙  你失败了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.11,0:21:06.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉  苍天少主
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.85,0:21:09.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  该不会就是这小子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.05,0:21:10.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.05,0:21:12.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就是对我下挑战书的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.69,0:21:14.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幕后主使苍天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.06,0:21:17.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.49,0:21:19.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.63,0:21:21.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好乖好乖
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.70,0:21:23.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭家伙  不要把我当小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.40,0:21:26.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是雷兽一族之长
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.17,0:21:26.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好~好~
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.70,0:21:28.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这样  不要摸我的额头
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.10,0:21:33.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就因为这小鬼\N我们就忙的不可开交
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.67,0:21:35.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是说过不需要帮忙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.18,0:21:37.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小弟弟  你几岁了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.41,0:21:38.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你太没礼貌了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.71,0:21:39.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不是小弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.78,0:21:40.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是女生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.28,0:21:45.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是女生吗  那更可爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.12,0:21:50.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫你不要摸我的额头
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.63,0:21:53.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女生…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.73,0:21:55.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她居然是女生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.76,0:21:58.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是有够可笑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.73,0:22:00.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.43,0:22:02.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  七宝  你想逃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.11,0:22:08.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你是承认输了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.68,0:22:10.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.11,0:22:13.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.55,0:22:19.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好孩子就当个好孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.92,0:22:23.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再想什么报仇了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.23,0:22:28.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样我的死斗结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.73,0:22:32.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我成功切断了复仇的宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.27,0:22:35.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那穷凶恶极的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.34,0:22:37.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,苍天跟红龙也受到了教训
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.64,0:22:40.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再也不敢找我决斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.09,0:22:58.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,经过了这一天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.29,0:23:01.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我成长了一大步或二大步
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.43,0:23:04.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是在我面前
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.30,0:23:06.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有更强的敌人等待着
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.87,0:23:07.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此我不能驻足
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.97,0:23:09.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不能回首过去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.94,0:23:10.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.70,0:23:13.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这正是背负着战斗之宿命的我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.34,0:23:15.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男子汉的生活方式
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.94,0:23:17.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再耍帅了  呆子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.08,0:23:21.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇  犬夜叉欺负我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.88,0:23:23.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬~夜~叉~
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.98,0:23:25.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.49,0:23:26.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.46,0:23:29.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呆子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.65,0:24:56.65,ED,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.75,0:23:40.35,ED,,0,0,0,,究竟要流多少泪{\fad(500,0)}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.00,0:23:47.20,ED,,0,0,0,,Every Heart 才能坦白面对自己呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.82,0:23:54.02,ED,,0,0,0,,倘若对谁传达情感
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.55,0:24:01.02,ED,,0,0,0,,Every Heart 是否就能得到满足呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.02,0:24:07.32,ED,,0,0,0,,害怕着漫长漫长的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.47,0:24:14.40,ED,,0,0,0,,朝着遥远的星星祈祷着
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.72,0:24:21.15,ED,,0,0,0,,在不停流转的时空之中
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.75,0:24:27.77,ED,,0,0,0,,我们都在寻找真正的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.25,0:24:34.82,ED,,0,0,0,,希望自己能够变得更坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.97,0:24:41.50,ED,,0,0,0,,今天也要抬头看着高高的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.80,0:24:48.12,ED,,0,0,0,,在不停流转的时空之中
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.60,0:24:54.75,ED,,0,0,0,,我们都在寻找生命的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.65,0:24:58.65,ED,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.20,0:25:09.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  那家伙怎么搞的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.77,0:25:10.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.80,0:25:12.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对大家说了你的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.94,0:25:13.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反而让误会更深了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.97,0:25:15.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不是管那些事的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.44,0:25:17.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落的分身又出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.41,0:25:19.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是误解归误解
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.41,0:25:22.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们只是觉得你是个不良少年
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.08,0:25:23.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙展开了无尽的杀戮
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.05,0:25:26.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从很多人身上夺走了脸
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.02,0:25:28.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次回 犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.49,0:25:30.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怖的无脸男人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.56,0:25:31.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.89,0:25:33.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“不凉少黏”是什么啊（不良少年）
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.40,0:25:37.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉宝典
